  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK662">
<l>ūṟorā luṟṟapi ṉolkāmaiyivviraṇṭi </l>
<l> ṉāṟeṉpa rāyntavar kōḷ</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Not to perform a ruinous act, and not to be discouraged by the ruinous termination of an act, are the two maxims which, the wise say, from the principles of those who have investigated the subject.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
